HEADWORD: Intermeddler
<hw>In`ter*med"dler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
meddles with, or intrudes into, the affairs of others.</def>
<rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
